com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.filtering

Class FilterNull<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.filtering.FilterNull<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - - Element type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Filter<E>

    public class FilterNull<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Filter<E>
    A filter that performs a simple NULL-Check on each element. If the element is null, True is returned indicating that it should be filtered.
